---
title: Sweet Chili Chicken Burgers with Lime-Garlic Aioli and Pickled Cucumber
description: We've fancied up the classic chicken burger with succulent chicken tenders, a sweet chili glaze, pickled cucumber and a fresh lime-garlic aioli — there's never a dull moment in this weeknight winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-de-poulet-au-chili-doux-81451a81.jpg
